==Bio==
"Rob Hopkins is an activist and writer on environmental issues, based in Totnes, England. He is best known as the founder and figurehead of the [[Transition Town Movement|Transition movement]], which he initiated in 2005. Hopkins has written four books on environmentalism and activism." ''[https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rob_Hopkins Wikipedia, 2018]''

